          <a
            href="#how-it-works"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/30 bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:bg-white/20"
          >
            See How It Works
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/60">
          No commitment. No pressure. Just a conversation about what's possible.
        </p>
